lead_paragraph: TAYLOR--Jane Keating. Not all the world's champagne could celebrate Jane's graciousness, sparkling wit and loving friendship. One final sip and then goodnight, sweets. With profound sympathy for Bob, Jason, Brigham, Stella, the twins and Solo. Judy Goldstein 1/3

headline.main: Paid Notice: Deaths  TAYLOR, JANE KEATING
